304
00:21:48.002 --> 00:21:50.118
- Lucien, watch me.

305
00:21:50.118 --> 00:21:52.951
(cheerful music)

306
00:22:02.979 --> 00:22:05.562
- Grandma Burnier Be careful.

307
00:22:08.106 --> 00:22:10.487
